label("$O_2$", O2, NE);
label("$O_3$", O3, SW);
label("$O_4$", O4, SE);
label("$O$", O, NW);
label("$P$", P, NE);
[/asy]

Note that $O_1 O_2 = 6,$ $O_3 O_4 = 4,$ and $O_1 O = 3 - r.$  Let $h$ denote the distance from $O$ to $AB.$

[asy]
